 be pleased with him, said, \u201cThat I take hold of them on peaceful terms\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20698,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/06\/15\/umar-nikah-righteous-spouse\/","url_meta":{"origin":17683,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Nikah: Nothing benefits like a righteous spouse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Umar ibn Al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNothing benefits a man, after faith in Allah, as much as a wife with good character, loving and fertile. Nothing harms a man, after unbelief in Allah, as much as a wife with evil character and a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/umar-on-hamd-how-are-you-all-praise-is-due-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17683,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Hamd: How are you? All praise is due to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man greeted Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, with peace and Umar returned his greeting. Then, Umar said to the man, \u201cHow are you?\u201d The man said, \u201cI praise Allah to you.\u201d Umar said, \u201cThis praise is what I wanted from you.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u